article_title: President: ‘Obamacare’ moniker OK cause I do care

article_metadata.description: Video on NBCNews.com: While addressing young people from around the country at the White House Youth Summit, President Obama jokes about the unofficial nickname bestowed on his Affordable Care Act and requests their help in spreading the word on how they can #getcovered.
article_metadata.title: President: ‘Obamacare’ moniker OK cause I do care
